&lt;li&gt;Babosa: &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/norman/babosa&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;external&quot;&gt;https://github.com/norman/babosa&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
